  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across five flow-speed combinations. Experiments were performed at an external test facility and validation comparisons were compiled; however, not all structured generation activity links were recorded in the evidence package at the time of submission. Full 13-factor assessment is included. Decision: Accepted.",
